# init(sessionDelegate:)

**Initializer**

Initializes a find interaction object with the delegate object you specify.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor init(sessionDelegate: any UIFindInteractionDelegate)
```

## Return Value

Returns a find interaction object with the associated delegate.

## Discussion

Create an object that conforms to the [doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIFindInteractionDelegate] protocol and assign it to this property.
